zinga.com/24/12/42452165/bitcoin-ethereum-dogecoin-spike-after-inflation-data-matches-expectations-top-analyst-foresees-new-btc-ath-if-it-"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"news","date":"2024-12-12","headline":"OVER 1,000 AMAZON WORKERS AT MAJOR WEST COAST AIR HUB JOIN TEAMSTERS UNION","id":"833589ca-8ce8-413c-8db7-2bbc75de180a","is_major":false,"source":"PR NewsWire","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":[],"time":"01:46:40","timestamp":"2024-12-12T01:46:40Z","url":"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/over-1-000-amazon-workers-at-major-west-coast-air-hub-join-teamsters-union-302329625.html"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"investing","date":"2024-12-12","headline":"China 7-day repo rate drops by 15 basis points to 1.6033%","id":"b3dd9960-6f72-4ee5-a6c1-a1094422acee","is_major":false,"source":"Tradex","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":[],"time":"01:45:41","timestamp":"2024-12-12T01:45:41Z","url":null},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"securities","date":"2024-12-12","headline":"DNP Achieves Fine Pattern Resolution on EUV Lithography Photomasks for Beyond 2nm Generation","id":"6cf1e7ce-75c4-4a15-92d5-1a8f66c29768","is_major":false,"source":"Business Wire","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":[],"time":"01:40:27","timestamp":"2024-12-12T01:40:27Z","url":"http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20241208160921/en/DNP-Achieves-Fine-Pattern-Resolution-on-EUV-Lithography-Photomasks-for-Beyond-2nm-Generation/?feedref=JjAwJuNHiystnCoBq_hl-Q-tiwWZwkcswR1UZtV7eGe24xL9TZOyQUMS3J72mJlQ7fxFuNFTHSunhvli30RlBNXya2izy9YOgHlBiZQk2LOzmn6JePCpHPCiYGaEx4DL1Rq8pNwkf3AarimpDzQGuQ=="},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"investing","date":"2024-12-12","headline":"PBOC to Issue 20 Billion Yuan Six-Month Bills in Hong Kong with HKMA","id":"e0989965-da43-4f95-9d4f-0cdba205b11a","is_major":false,"source":"Tradex","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":[],"time":"01:37:07","timestamp":"2024-12-12T01:37:07Z","url":null},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"cr